&lt;p&gt;比如在网页中:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;script async src=&#34;//jsfiddle.net/roumtchz/6/embed/js,html,result/dark/&#34;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/ikeq/hexo-filter-mathjax-ssr&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;Mathjax-SSR&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;
